{"tid":39384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★毒撚住公屋無得輸！化成白骨都有㐆署照顧！","createTime":"2016-12-14T14:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T15:03:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46e608b38990fd2b30abf8c919ac2a0433778f23","tid":39384,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】深水埗富昌邨揭發罕見「白骨命案」，房署職員破門收屋，揭發屋內有一副白骨屍骸。涉案單位位於富誠樓，房署指租戶連續兩月未有繳交租金，按程序派員前往收回單位。消息稱，昨早10時許，房署職員破門進入屋，赫見牀上躺着一副森森白骨，由保安員報警<br />\n<br />\n死者為獨居上址的84歲姓楊老翁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/八旬翁欠租%20%20房署爆門收屋檢白骨/web_tc/article/20150415/s00002/1429035171420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%85%AB%E6%97%AC%E7%BF%81%E6%AC%A0%E7%A7%9F%2520%2520%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E7%88%86%E9%96%80%E6%94%B6%E5%B1%8B%E6%AA%A2%E7%99%BD%E9%AA%A8%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150415%2Fs00002%2F1429035171420&d=TZJzgzLzhUqlVqOCkDfb2QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=bced3b61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%85%AB%E6%97%AC%E7%BF%81%E6%AC%A0%E7%A7%9F%2520%2520%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E7%88%86%E9%96%80%E6%94%B6%E5%B1%8B%E6%AA%A2%E7%99%BD%E9%AA%A8%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150415%2Fs00002%2F1429035171420&h=8c39965d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/八旬翁欠租%20%20房署爆門收屋檢白骨/web_tc/article/20150415/s00002/1429035171420</a>"},{"pid":"c927e7f3e98b7dd43ba1abfbdfd9f89b8270d643","tid":39384,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197c0629722d414f444d430b780316610356f2fe","tid":39384,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab40c802